snippet.title: Amber lashes out at Britney for always siding with the Villalunas | Nang Ngumiti Ang Langit
snippet.description:
Mikmik (Sophia Reola) resolves to seek Britney's (Heart Ramos) help in finding the person who posted the video defaming her family. (With English Subtitles)
